cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CR, cs.IT 

The paper deals with learning from data, which is a core topic in machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves privacy-preserving techniques (cs.CR) and deals with the issue of variable quality of data (cs.AI, cs.DS). Additionally, the use of stochastic gradient algorithms is a common optimization technique in machine learning (cs.IT).
